{"tid":1570442,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 11 Pro 原來有 6GB RAM !","createTime":"2019-09-15T05:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T09:20:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"17ae1724997f5ccfd3258870c4d2c076e0e6bfb8","tid":1570442,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"iPhone 11 系列即將開賣，當然大家最關心當然是到底新機的實際規格。因為 Apple 從來在發表會上只能會提及新處理器，但新機到底有幾多 RAM，電池有幾大 ? 一般要等外國有跑分，或是有拆機報告才會知道。不過根據外國爆料達人 OnLeaks 的消息，今次 iPhone 11 Pro 及 Pro Max 原來會有 6GB RAM，而電池容量亦會增加不少。根據 Apple 在發表會上表示，iPhone 11 Pro 及 Pro Max 在電池的效能會比起上代 Xs 及 Xs Max 更長，分別多 4小時間及 5 小時，不過有趣是 11 Pro Max 的電池的確比起 Xs Max 多了 326 mAh，但真的足以令手機續航了增加 5 小時嗎 ?<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2593%25B7%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%2595%25AB%25E9%259D%25A2-90.png&h=2f931b5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bad1afd7e89a7bf46ddd838defcfb79d87edbd2b","tid":1570442,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/09/13/iphone-11-pro-%e5%8e%9f%e4%be%86%e6%9c%89-6gb-ram/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F13%2Fiphone-11-pro-%25e5%258e%259f%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%259c%2589-6gb-ram%2F&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=9b1a6461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/09/13/iphone-11-pro-%e5%8e%9f%e4%be%86%e6%9c%89-6gb-ram/</a>"},{"pid":"6ccf50f4767d5ab49bc695e6487a8a171becff53","tid":1570442,"uid":216354,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"bad1afd7e89a7bf46ddd838defcfb79d87edbd2b","tid":1570442,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"<a 